reviews.review_text:
SirMick Does It Again Thank You SirMick.  The sound on this is Great.

The boys were really "on" this night.

"Mason's Children" is the highlight for me.
A Carnival of Sound!!!!!!!!!!!!! A true gem! China is fierce. Jerry's playing.OMFG!!!!!

In the wake of the Fillmore This is a decent show, following the double night stand at the Fillmore East.  The brevity of their songs is peculiar, but can be refreshing as well.  I wouldn't call this show essential for the tour but if you're a big fan of early 70 Dead than it's one for the pile.

Follow the tour: 1970
